own.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n 你係度食飯盒就話姐<br />\n冇理由飲水都唔得掛<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申未試過係車廂食嘢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪飲緊水先而家？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我意思如果唔係太大模廝樣<br />\n通常都隻眼開隻眼閉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n飲緊咩根本唔係重點<br />\n你睇唔過眼咪去舉報佢囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n捉埋晒啲字眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"931751b994ace06b33e8314c55b18943312fd4ae","tid":48262,"uid":54862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T04:04:16.000Z","msg":"男黎架吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個樣唔得 負皮"},{"pid":"d54cbc827725647e2fa79ea372d1f8e69db58d9c","tid":48262,"uid":10084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T04:08:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbc1127b1f3466101caf6670973d226dd0f573d3","tid":48262,"uid":60082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T04:15:37.000Z","msg":"無啦啦影人做乜撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 竟然冇人屌"},{"pid":"c455ee29382fefc939bcaead73f35b530a51f354","tid":48262,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T04:20:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無啦啦影人做乜撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 竟然冇人屌</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n影街外人不嬲都冇人屌㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係影絲打 狗公行為先屌咋嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家都唔想身份曝光 所以影自己人唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc75fc34d2420c13a91488a52d92a4514558b8c1","tid":48262,"uid":67752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T04:30:27